title: The Gary Null Show
content:
Guest: Christiane Northrup Dr. <!--more--> Christiane Northrup is a board-certified OB/GYN physician and is regarded by many doctors, alternative physicians and women as a leading pioneer and visionary in women’s health and the biology and lifestyle associated with menopause.
 She is graduate of Darthmouth Medical School, undertook her residency at Tufts University New England Medical Center, and was a clinical professor of OBGYN at Maine’s Medical Center for 20 years.
Dr Northrup’s research and practice based upon the a body-mind-spirit paradigm.
She is the authored two NY Times best-sellers has received numerous awards for her research, publications and private practice Christiane’s best selling “Wisdom of Menopause: Creating Physical and Emotional Health During the Change” has recently been updated and republished.
